snippet.title: Skin Deep announcement trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist Skin Deep on Steam!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/301280

Skin Deep is an immersive first-person shooter. We got sneezing. We got things getting stuck in your feet. Stalk through a starship and sneak, subvert, and sabotage in this stellar sandbox.

You're outnumbered, outgunned, and have no shoes. Welcome to Skin Deep!

• SITE: http://blendogames.com/skindeep
• DEV STREAMS (Every weekday at 10AM PT):  http://twitch.tv/blendogames
• EMAIL NEWSLETTER: http://blendogames.com/newsletter
• DISCORD: http://discord.gg/blendogames
• TWITTER: http://twitter.com/blendogames
